WEBVTT

00:06:57.667 --> 00:07:02.351
bolalarimizning ma'lumoti yig'ilganda 
biz bu texnologiyalarga ishona olamizmi?

00:07:02.375 --> 00:07:03.625
Aniq ishona olamizmi?

00:07:05.708 --> 00:07:06.958
Mening javobim "yo'q."

00:07:07.792 --> 00:07:09.059
Antropolog sifatida,

00:07:09.083 --> 00:07:12.851
Sun'iy ong va bashorat tahlillari
ajoyibdir.

00:07:12.875 --> 00:07:14.893
Kasallik izini topishda

00:07:14.917 --> 00:07:16.750
yoki iqlim o'zgarishga
qarshi kurashda.

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:19.643
Bu qarashdan
voz kechishimiz kerak:

00:07:19.667 --> 00:07:23.351
ularning xolisona ma'lumot yig'ishida

00:07:23.375 --> 00:07:26.559
va dalillarga asoslanib qaror chiqarishda
ularga ishonishimizda,

00:07:26.583 --> 00:07:28.476
insonlar hayoti haqida.

00:07:28.500 --> 00:07:31.059
Chunki ular insonning aslini ko'rsatmaydi.